metadata.name: AOL.084
metadata.description:
High-fidelity digital painting of the portrait of Dream Angel: AOL.084.

While alive, they exist in-between worlds, altruistically ushering lost souls trapped in the void of interdimensional travels, to and from their dreams.

The Dream Angels are based on intricately personal details about a recurring dream I've had since a child.

Only now, through the magic of AI and Machine Learning have I been able to bring them into this realm in exquisite detail, exactly how I remember them from the other side.

Size - 3333x3333px.
Resolution - 333 ppi.
Software - Adobe Photoshop Version: 23.4.2 & AI.

Available only on foundation.app by @artsea.
